Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.21,0:00:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我是村上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.58,0:00:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我在抽煙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.19,0:00:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,計算錯誤?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.69,0:00:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,現在才講?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.46,0:00:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,誰的題?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.43,0:00:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,星奈?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.54,0:00:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,好我現在回去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.87,0:01:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,被丈夫的上司侵犯七天\N我失去了理性星奈愛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.64,0:01:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,一週前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.38,0:01:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,夏威夷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.71,0:01:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,要去是可以啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.82,0:01:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.39,0:01:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我早點回去掰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.56,0:01:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,跟誰講話?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.63,0:01:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,妻子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.63,0:01:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,真恩愛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.63,0:01:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,講清楚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.07,0:01:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒見你太太耶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.34,0:02:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,三
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.11,0:02:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我有照片
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.28,0:02:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.72,0:02:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,下個月是結婚紀念日
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.19,0:02:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.76,0:02:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你還沒結婚?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.06,0:02:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.27,0:02:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,婚很棒唷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.40,0:02:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.60,0:02:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,老公怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.87,0:03:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉我今天要開會
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.84,0:03:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼突然
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.37,0:03:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,會很晚回家嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.01,0:03:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道耶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.45,0:03:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,是唷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.08,0:03:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你最近都沒睡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.98,0:03:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,小心身體唷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.42,0:03:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我幫你做便當
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.92,0:03:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.42,0:03:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,早怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.03,0:03:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.10,0:03:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我馬上去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.87,0:03:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉我今晚可能不回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.45,0:04:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,便當呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.58,0:04:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,喂?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.71,0:04:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.45,0:04:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,老公?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.22,0:04:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.49,0:04:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.57,0:04:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.09,0:05:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,老公
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.04,0:05:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,部長
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.74,0:05:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,他很累吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.38,0:05:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.69,0:05:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我去叫他不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.89,0:05:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我今天有話要跟妳說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.87,0:06:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,其實
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.60,0:06:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,他現在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.67,0:06:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,快被公司炒了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.81,0:06:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,他最近狀態很差
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.55,0:06:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,現在這樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.62,0:06:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,還是先別告訴他了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.12,0:06:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,到底怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.26,0:06:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,他沒說嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.14,0:06:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,他在工作上出了大錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.47,0:06:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,害公司損失重
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.95,0:06:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,所以公司想炒了他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.58,0:06:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,他為了彌補
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.02,0:06:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,才會這麼累
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.22,0:07:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,但是他每天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.39,0:07:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,都努力工作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.23,0:07:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不過是出一次錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.03,0:07:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,***
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.44,0:07:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不只一次
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.51,0:07:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,能幫點忙嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.48,0:07:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.18,0:07:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.52,0:07:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我什麼都願意做
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.26,0:07:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.59,0:07:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,只有你能幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.60,0:07:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,太太
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.11,0:07:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,妳什麼都做?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.71,0:07:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.42,0:07:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.75,0:08:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,結婚一年還有房
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.72,0:08:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.50,0:08:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.73,0:08:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我該怎麼辦?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.60,0:08:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我來幫他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.25,0:08:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,真的?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.85,0:08:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.62,0:08:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,***
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.49,0:08:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,妳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.12,0:08:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.69,0:08:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是這意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.06,0:08:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,妳懂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.54,0:08:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,要是妳不配合
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.84,0:08:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,他就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.84,0:08:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,懂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.84,0:09:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.65,0:09:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,聽話妳自己說的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.75,0:09:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,***
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.55,0:09:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,只有我可以幫他了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.32,0:09:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以幫忙說話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.03,0:09:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,他能不能重回公司
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.50,0:09:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,全部都得
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.03,0:09:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,看我幫不幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.31,0:09:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.71,0:09:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,想幫他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.98,0:09:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,-住手  我才\N-只有這方法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.68,0:09:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,才能幫他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.79,0:09:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,妳想害他被炒嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.62,0:09:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.62,0:09:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我很柔的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.83,0:09:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.50,0:09:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,妳要配合嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.17,0:10:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.67,0:10:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,要是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.78,0:10:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,他丟工作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.31,0:10:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你現在的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.42,0:10:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,還有房子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.19,0:10:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,都會消失
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.73,0:10:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他被炒掉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.43,0:10:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,這些都會消失
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.01,0:10:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,***Empty
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.47,0:10:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,所以還是聽話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.75,0:10:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,幸好妳很美
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.65,0:10:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.11,0:11:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.45,0:11:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,只要把身體
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.85,0:11:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,借我一段時
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.22,0:11:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,太太
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.73,0:11:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,幫他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.26,0:11:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我當然會幫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.67,0:11:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,只有我可以幫他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.08,0:11:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,還有妳的誠意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.96,0:12:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,他在那邊?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.34,0:12:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,那換地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.77,0:12:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.68,0:12:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我很溫柔的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.33,0:12:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,去別的房胃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.07,0:12:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,別出聲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.30,0:13:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,在這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.07,0:13:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,也不錯唷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.81,0:13:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.61,0:13:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,幫幫他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.55,0:13:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不用一直說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.99,0:13:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,要看妳的誠意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.14,0:14:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,伸舌頭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.40,0:14:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,很好唷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.82,0:15:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.59,0:15:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.79,0:15:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,這是為了他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.16,0:15:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,要聽話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.10,0:15:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,他會不會被炒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.68,0:15:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,都要靠妳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.75,0:15:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,漂亮的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.05,0:15:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,懂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.31,0:16:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,腿張開
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.60,0:16:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,想幫他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.30,0:16:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.74,0:16:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,想保護他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.51,0:16:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,那就聽話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.62,0:16:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,主導權在我手上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.60,0:17:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,自己脫掉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.09,0:17:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,好美
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.96,0:18:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,夠了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.17,0:18:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不用怕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.07,0:18:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我很溫柔的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.64,0:18:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,妳看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.03,0:18:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,好美
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.33,0:19:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,好過份
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.16,0:19:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,真敏感
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.37,0:20:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.01,0:20:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,這不是背叛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.95,0:20:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,***是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.29,0:20:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,妳為了保護他
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.76,0:20:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣想就沒有罪惡感
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.13,0:20:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,可以享受了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.60,0:20:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.17,0:20:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不是妳的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.98,0:20:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我很溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.85,0:20:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,好美
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.15,0:20:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.43,0:21:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,脫掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.23,0:21:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.12,0:21:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,換這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.62,0:22:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.50,0:22:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.87,0:22:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你們有做嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.94,0:22:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,跟你無關
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.88,0:22:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,好像是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.48,0:22:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,但我想聽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.32,0:22:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.93,0:22:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,好美
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.63,0:22:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,爽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.30,0:22:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,才沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.24,0:22:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,可是妳在發抖
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.20,0:23:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.07,0:23:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,越來越溼了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.41,0:23:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.76,0:23:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,妳聽
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.12,0:24:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.69,0:24:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,爽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.39,0:24:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.18,0:25:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,想要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.02,0:25:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.75,0:25:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,好美
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.69,0:25:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,好色唷
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.56,0:25:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,配他太浪費了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.10,0:26:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,好溼
